{"tid":1352033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文]地產商會幫大家力阻解放軍","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T07:58:04.000Z","uid":267494,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb30e17de0c10990421b9ce23aba00862f83fd5","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"繼續俾何妖呢啲冚家產搞事，只要我地唔好退縮，我敢肯定，樓價大跌之下，一眾地產商自然會收何妖皮，再迫供林鄭<br />\n<br />\n講真，解放軍入城，你同我都唔會有好日子過，但地產商呢啲貪心小人，上通北京權力核心，會願意坐以待斃捨割投資左既幾千億？抑或力挽狂瀾或暗或明製止動亂？<br />\n<br />\n我俾幾個例子大家<br />\n<br />\n市傳中半山波老道21號，即將會推售，當年長實投地開支近120億，每呎樓價未連建築達到26000，你估長實要出手搞，會搞示威者抑或何妖呢啲牛鬼蛇神？<br />\n<br />\n仲有太多唔例明投資額啦，寫幾個算<br />\ncentral peak, 司徒拔道18號<br />\n啟德(大量中資投左地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n黃竹坑一帶至深灣各個天價地段<br />\n<br />\n所以呢鋪showhand，大家唔洗驚<br />\n<br />\nIf we burn,  you burn with us<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50b3b1a8e9fbd53820cfcd657107fcb638cb277","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31097408138021399752da187dec23c2339dbede","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"推，大家唔洗怕解放軍，啲有錢佬會被迫頂住<br />\n<br />\n若呢個機會今次都散左，一定有大清算，我地無乜退路嫁啦"},{"pid":"54afce47b4ef9f4496a5c0f3cf8454d9367befc3","tid":1352033,"uid":276365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:23:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c908a17a8610d72530d4440a2ad9575671b3846d","tid":1352033,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"U ! Burn with us"},{"pid":"b389aed9a56305a2a8603187bc5720d66a18df13","tid":1352033,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:29:06.000Z","msg":"*動物台版塊使用權公投*<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351378\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n動物台動議成功，上環事件有關討論可到動物台進行，以減少資訊混亂<br />\n<br />\n見字請幫忙copy宣傳"},{"pid":"8a12229bdc8ceff511136fce48636f10cf94df4b","tid":1352033,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"其實各大發展商表面上支持送中 or扮中立，但其實佢地係咪反對？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a5f3cb3baeea57ff03cdf538bf42da6d41a7f4","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:32:06.000Z","msg":"仲有，共產黨內部從外睇好似好團結，但一講到要大家跌幾千億，諗都唔洗諗所知結局啦<br />\n<br />\n江派無幾千億，佢會當無事發生？<br />\n胡撚塗難道有鋪癮鐘意跌錢？<br />\n影帝溫又幾時做左燒錢專員？<br />\n<br />\n用下腦都知，解放軍只會係紙老虎<br />\n<br />\n你共產黨就算壓倒本地薑，仲要鬼打鬼，再有美帝差一腳埋黎，到時殺牛屎佬+林鄭易，抑或殺幾十萬個示威者會快速恢復秩序，傻既都計到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1c1a8fd3af9fa92f79a855adfd68a618106c03","tid":1352033,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:35:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e78a5444c3db4c1c1fe4385e960868c9e53cd349","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a12229bdc8ceff511136fce48636f10cf94df4b","tid":1352033,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"其實各大發展商表面上支持送中 or扮中立，但其實佢地係咪反對？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"大劉話左你聽佢點睇<br />\n我個人估佢可能有份捐錢反送中添啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157d867a7c3381213635be07589780cd847115ce","tid":1352033,"uid":169074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f97aeb92f378913a5208d2ab3b5c20b5a9e89133","tid":1352033,"uid":224630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"但係如果共產黨畀大陸同一帶一路嘅地產佢哋等價交換呢？"},{"pid":"62f74455338b1d176208b06b4d540c01056cf307","tid":1352033,"uid":91721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:45:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有大量中資企業用香港樓同股做抵壓<br />\n一出解放軍<br />\n中國債務泡沫</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即刻爆炸</span>"},{"pid":"ce45bce52c35010eb9edcbf4477c9661883aadcf","tid":1352033,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"班支國地產商用香港借落一堆美元債<br />\n無香港做再融資<br />\n<br />\n俾債主溶咗都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d664d5fa9b24ef0264962ef846211c4b68ddde","tid":1352033,"uid":179679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a12229bdc8ceff511136fce48636f10cf94df4b","tid":1352033,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"其實各大發展商表面上支持送中 or扮中立，但其實佢地係咪反對？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af53d2d434789238c43e4ba7189a85939380a0c","tid":1352033,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97aeb92f378913a5208d2ab3b5c20b5a9e89133","tid":1352033,"uid":224630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"但係如果共產黨畀大陸同一帶一路嘅地產佢哋等價交換呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:51:28.000Z","msg":"你覺得班人會信共產黨？<br />\n共產黨最叻係咩？空頭支票講大話呀<br />\n哩刻比佢地 第日一樣照收番唔洗理由"},{"pid":"77e8a1fa7ad564284d18c064b80d1d7f51bc84c0","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f97aeb92f378913a5208d2ab3b5c20b5a9e89133","tid":1352033,"uid":224630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"但係如果共產黨畀大陸同一帶一路嘅地產佢哋等價交換呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:52:08.000Z","msg":"你大我呀？哈薩克斯坦？烏茲別克？<br />\n要搞幾多野，重新佈幾多局先有今日菁雋呢啲濕鳩龍床盤都賺到笑既項目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b7851efd8ab77d3106af500a8f45334eccb454","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:36:52.000Z","msg":"晨早一推，希望大家唔好怕<br />\n<br />\n合眾之力，地產商唔係同路人，但會有一個位連地產商都要被迫出手做野保住自已利益<br />\n<br />\n大家記住，正因為你無足輕重，所以整治你一個係無用<br />\n<br />\n但何妖之流唔同，擒賊先擒王，而且係金錢傭兵，係可收買對像<br />\n<br />\n你的每一步 動搖獨栽一大步<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9cf7001e6bada3c144fcf357bbfba3b9e8da29","tid":1352033,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:45:05.000Z","msg":"所以根本唔洗驚<br />\n香港咁多商家佬<br />\n佢地仲驚過我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6595a58dc56c7fede26c7e3de58119660d811e","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf13fc90dff99c455865889d7923dda1efc3f69","tid":1352033,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}